-- Putin says Russia will not stint on spending for 2018 World Cup
-- By Vladimir Soldatkin
-- Thu Dec 18, 2014 05:39AM EST
-- None



MOSCOW, Dec 18 (Reuters) - Russian President Vladimir Putin said Russia would not stint on spending money to stage the soccer World Cup in 2018 at an end-of-year news conference on Thursday.   (Reporting by Vladimir Soldatkin; Writing by Alexander Winning, editing by Elizabeth Piper)  ((alexander.winning@thomsonreuters.com; +7 495 775 1242; Reuters Messaging: alexander.winning.thomsonreuters.com@reuters.net))  Keywords: RUSSIA CRISIS/PUTIN SOCCER

